data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to this beautiful home nestled in a charming community, conveniently located near parks and schools. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the fresh paint on the main floor! The heart of the home is the spacious kitchen, boasting ample cabinet and counter space. It seamlessly opens to the living room, creating a warm and inviting space for family gatherings. For more formal occasions, the dining room offers an elegant option. Upstairs, the primary bedroom is a true retreat with higher ceilings and an ensuite bath featuring dual sinks, shower, and soaking tub for ultimate relaxation. Additionally, the primary suite offers two closets, ensuring plenty of storage space. The second floor also features a large and versatile game room, a flexible space for your needs. Outside, the fully fenced backyard includes a covered patio and a storage shed, making it a fantastic outdoor space for all your activities.
